ENTRY            F1270   20260117   20260508   20260508       F108
SUBENT        F1270001   20260117   20260508   20260508       F108
BIB                 10         23
TITLE      Fusion-fission and quasifission of superheavy systems
           with Z=10-116 formed in Ca-48 induced reactions
AUTHOR     (E.M.Kozulin,G.N.Knyazheva,I.M.Itkis,M.G.Itkis,
           A.A.Bogachev,E.V.Chernysheva,L.Krupa,F.Hanappe,
           O.Dorvaux,L.Stuttge,W.H.Trzaska,C.Schmitt,G.Chubarian)
INSTITUTE  (4ZZZDUB) Flerov Laboratory of Nuclear Reactions
           (2BLGBRU,2FR STR,2FR ULP,2SF JYV,2FR GAN,1USATAM)
REFERENCE  (J,PR/C,90,054608,2014)
           #doi:10.1103/PhysRevC.90.054608
FACILITY   (CYCLO,4ZZZDUB) U-400 cyclotron
INC-SOURCE Beam intensity was in the range 2-3 pnA.
DETECTOR   (SPEC,PS,MCPLT) Time-of-flight double-arm spectrometer
           consists of start and stop four position sensitive
           detectors based on microchannel plates. The start
           detectors were placed at a distance of 4 cm from the
           target. The distance between start and stop detectors
           was 14 cm.
METHOD     (COINC,TOF)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information about source of uncertainties
HISTORY    (20151105C)
           (20260117U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
           MISC1-ERR deleted (uncertainty in digitizing was
           included in E-EXC-C-ER).
ENDBIB              23
