BIB                  4         10
REACTION   (94-PU-244(20-CA-48,FUS),,SIG,,MSC)
           Capture cross section (a sum of quasi-fission, compound
           nucleus fission and evaporation residue cross section)
           is given.
SAMPLE     Layer of Pu-244 with 180-220 ug/cm2 thickness was
           deposited on a 40-50 ug/cm2 carbon backing.
STATUS     (CURVE,,E.M.Kozulin+,J,PR/C,90,054608,2014) Fig. 11(b).
           No response from authors was received.
HISTORY    (20260117U) SD: BIB updated. MISC2-ERR -> E-EXC-C-ER;
           MISC1-ERR deleted.
